{"title":"沉船","authors":["金志伟"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":5,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金志伟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报载：一九九七年一月二十八日，沉没了五十八年的一代名舰“中山舰”在长江被打捞出水……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我的眼中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一天的长江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一道被再次撕裂的伤口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疼痛是一种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好遥远好遥远的感觉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你钢铁的身躯比铁更沉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我受伤的眼里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骤然深刻起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是五十八年前的炮火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灼伤了我的目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就像一把钥匙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在早春的阳光中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再次打开历史的重门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经听见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想洞开的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那声音好沉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那曾经血雨腥风的天空好沉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好沉的还有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血液中涌来的一阵又一阵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呐喊与呻吟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洒在那张发黄的病历上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掷地有声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掷地有声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我们再次打捞历史时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成亿束炽热的目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渐渐暖着你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒彻的躯体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我坚信："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永不生锈的是历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，耳畔再次响起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一位伟人的名言："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“忘记过去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就意味着背叛”……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}